body:
Riot: &quot;You want buffs right? Coming right up!&quot; - 
ADC mains: &quot;No, we wanted you to nerf damage and snowballing so games aren&#039;t over at 20 minutes&quot;
Riot: &quot;Yep, you got it, we overshot on the ADC nerfs and now we&#039;re buffing you back up so that everyone can make you the scapegoat for ruining SR&#039;s game pace!&quot;
ADC mains: &quot;...goddammit. The ride never ends.&quot;

Since Riot will never fix the pace of the game because esports or something, I guess the best we can hope for is for Riot to break our class for a couple months.
